lah-selves-family\/","url_meta":{"origin":25789,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Duties: Rights of Allah, your family, and yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Juhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, made a fellowship between Salman and Abu Darda. Salman visited Abu Darda and found his wife Umm Darda dressed in worn-out clothing. He asked her why she was like this. She said, \u201cYour brother Abu Darda is not interested\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37343,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/09\/abu-darda-bidah\/","url_meta":{"origin":25789,"position":1},"title":"Abu Darda on Bid\u2019ah: Anger at seeing innovations in the religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 9, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Darda reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, entered upon me while he was furious. I said, \u201cWhy are you angry?\u201d Abu Darda said, \u201cBy Allah, I do not recognize any of the affairs of Muhammad among them except that they pray in congregation.\u201d Source: al-Bida' li-Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22894,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/05\/09\/abu-darda-dua-akhlaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":25789,"position":2},"title":"Abu Darda on Akhlaq: Supplicating all night for good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Darda reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with them both, stood praying and weeping, saying, \u201cO Allah, you have made my form excellent, so make my character excellent.\u201d He continued until the morning and I said, \u201cO Abu Darda, you did not supplicate for anything but good character!\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3751,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/23\/abu-darda-hate-his-sinful-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":25789,"position":3},"title":"Abu Darda on Sinners: Hate his sinful deeds, do not abuse him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qilaba reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, passed by\u00a0a man who was being beaten because of his sin and they were cursing\u00a0him. Abu Darda\u00a0said, \u201cWhat do you think if he had fallen into a well. Would you not try to rescue him?\u201d They said yes.\u00a0Abu Darda\u00a0said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37895,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/18\/abu-darda-tafakkur\/","url_meta":{"origin":25789,"position":4},"title":"Umm Darda on Tafakkur: Abu Darda\u2019s habit of contemplation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Awn ibn Abdullah reported: I said to Umm Darda, may Allah be pleased with her, \u201cWhat act of worship did Abu Darda perform most often?\u201d Umm Darda said, \u201cReflection and consideration.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd wal-Raqa\u0304\u2019iq 286 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064f\u0644\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0644\u0650\u0623\u064f\u0645\u0650\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0639\u0650\u0628\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064e\u0629\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26968,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/12\/30\/abu-darda-following-nafs\/","url_meta":{"origin":25789,"position":5},"title":"Abu Darda on Ego: One who follows his ego harms himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 30, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Hasan reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \"Whoever follows his ego in everything he sees in people, his sadness will be lengthened and his rage will not be healed.\" Source: al-Muda\u0304ra\u0304h al-Na\u0304s 27 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u064e\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064f\u062a\u0652\u0628\u0650\u0639\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0633\u064e